Alhaji Omolaja Yisa, National Union of Road Transport Workers (NURTW) secretariat Chief Accountant at Abattoir, Agege, has denied the reports stating that the newly constituted Parks Management Committee (PMC), Musiliu Aknisaya, popularly called MC Oluomo, sacked all of them. The Secretariat’s Chief Accountant, disclosed this at a briefing, expressing that the rumours are targeted at tarnishing the image of Akinsanya. He said, “Since the advent of the Alhaji Akinsanya-led administration, no worker has been laid off for whatsoever reason, even those that engaged in activities that are contrary to the dictates of the union, were reprimanded and pardoned. “I must say that it is under Akinsanya’s administration, that the welfare of staff is adequately taken care of; staff salaries and enumerations were greatly enhanced.”